    "headline": "Hasbro (HAS) Q1 2026 Earnings Call Transcript",
    "summary": "Hasbro started 2026 with momentum, revenue grew 13%, powered by Wizards of the Coast, while Consumer Products posted point-of-sale growth and share gains across our key gem squared categories.  Q1 showed that Magic's record 2025 was no fluke.  Lorwyn Eclipsed, which debuted in January, became the best-selling Magic Premier set of all time and delivered the highest engagement in organized play statistics we've seen since the pandemic.",
